00:30:36,436 --> 00:30:38,816
And when you call
completePayment and pass


622
00:30:38,816 --> 00:30:41,806
in Success, you get
this nice check mark


623
00:30:42,016 --> 00:30:44,166
and the sheet will be dismissed.


