861
00:42:38,686 --> 00:42:41,226
to show they've seen
drastic conversion increases


862
00:42:41,226 --> 00:42:44,066
when they place the Apple Pay
button on their product page.


863
00:42:44,746 --> 00:42:46,306
Now obviously you
can also place it


